<p class="ayah 41-30" id="30" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبُّنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Our Lord,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) Allah,`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ثُمَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱسْتَقَـٰمُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">stand firm -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَتَنَزَّلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will descend</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">on them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Angels,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Do not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَخَافُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">fear,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and (do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَحْزَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">grieve</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَبْشِرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but receive the glad tidings</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْجَنَّةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of Paradise</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّتِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">which</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُنتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you were</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُوعَدُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">promised.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>30<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
