rst rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and for you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">therein</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَدَّعُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you ask,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>31<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 41-32" id="32" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نُزُلاً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">A hospitable gift</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">غَفُورٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Oft-Forgiving,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَّحِيمٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Most Merciful.`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>32<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 41-33" id="33" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَحْسَنُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) better</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَوْلاً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(in) speech</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّمَّن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">than (one) who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">دَعَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">invites</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَمِلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and does</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">صَـٰلِحًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">righteous (deeds)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and says,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّنِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Indeed, I am</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُ