<p class="ayah 41-34" id="34" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَسْتَوِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">are equal</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْحَسَنَةُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the good (deed)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّيِّئَةُ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the evil (deed).</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱدْفَعْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Repel</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلَّتِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">by (that) which</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هِىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[it]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَحْسَنُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) better;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then behold!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">One who,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَيْنَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">between you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَبَيْنَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and between him,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَدَٲوَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(was) enmity,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَأَنَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">as if he</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلِىٌّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(was) a friend</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَمِيمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">intimate.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>34<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 41-35" id="35" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُلَقَّـٰهَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it is granted</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">صَبَرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) patient</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُلَقَّـٰهَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it is granted</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذُو</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to the) owner</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَظٍّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) fortune</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَظِيمٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">great.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>35<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
